trans-unit.source: Contains the settings for the supported versions of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Bevat de instellingen voor de ondersteunde versies van het protocol WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: There are currently two versions of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol supported by [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 and WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.
trans-unit.target: Momenteel zijn er twee versies van het WS-ReliableMessaging-protocol dat wordt ondersteund door [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 en WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.

trans-unit.source: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 is returned by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A> and WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 is returned by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A>.
trans-unit.target: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 wordt geretourneerd door <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A>en WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 wordt geretourneerd door <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A>

trans-unit.source: Returns the default version of WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
An instance derived from <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"></xref> that represents the default version of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Een exemplaar is afgeleid van <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"> </xref> die staat voor de standaardversie van het protocol WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: Gets version 1.1 of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Hiermee haalt u versie 1.1 van het protocol WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"></xref> that represents the WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 version.
trans-unit.target: Een exemplaar is afgeleid van <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"> </xref> die staat voor de WS-ReliableMessaging1.1-versie.

trans-unit.source: Gets the February 2005 version of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Hiermee haalt u de versie van het protocol WS-ReliableMessaging februari 2005.

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"></xref> that represents the WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 version.
trans-unit.target: Een exemplaar is afgeleid van <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"> </xref> die staat voor de WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005-versie.
